data.description: This nice bi-level home will help you keep cool in the summer with it's stucco and AC.   Adding to the charm and practicality of this home is a large covered deck with a great sunrise view and a large fenced-in backyard.  Nice layout with 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom on each level.  There is a living room on the main level and a family room on the lower level.  New carpet and paint on both floors.  Close to schools, parks, shopping, and restaurants.  Within 7 Miles of both Fort Carson and Peterson Air Force Base.
